		  cavities, a normal conducting 7-cell PETRA-III RF-cavity
		  structure has been installed with the goal to store an
		  average current of 25 mA. In this paper we discuss our
		  analysis of coupled-bunch instabilities driven by the
		  Higher Order Modes (HOMs) of the 7-cell PETRA-III
